caption:
Satan didn’t just go after Eve—he went after the first marriage.
Why? Because marriage is holy.
It reflects Christ.
It brings life.
It humbles us before God.
That’s why the enemy still wages war against it today.
Fight for your marriage like your faith depends on it—because it does.
.
